he assay described below, such as Bay 60-7550 (Ki-˜0.2 nM) at 1 μM concentration for 100% inhibition. Bay 60-7550 was obtained from Axxora via Fisher Scientific (cat#ALX-270-421-M025/cat#NC9314773). Put another way, any compound with Ki of ˜0.2 to about 2 nM could be used at 1 to 10 μM. 0% of inhibition is determined by using DMSO (1% final concentrations).






